Info.Title: Star Trek
Info.Writer: Roberto Orci, Alex Kurtzman, Gene Roddenberry (television series "Star Trek")
Info.Actors: Chris Pine, Zachary Quinto, Leonard Nimoy, Eric Bana
Info.Plot: The brash James T. Kirk tries to live up to his father's legacy with Mr. Spock keeping him in check as a vengeful Romulan from the future creates black holes to destroy the Federation one planet at a time.
